modules.description: Provides set operations such as union, intersection, and difference on integer sets, with efficient membership checking and insertion. Works with custom set structures optimized for small to medium-sized collections. Used to manage unique identifiers in a game engine's entity system and track active user sessions in a server application.

Provides functions to retrieve and set the CPU core affinity of the current process. Operates with integer values representing processor core numbers. Used to control process execution on specific CPU cores for performance or resource management purposes.
